BP Plc (BP/)  started drilling exploratory
wells at the Risha natural-gas deposit in  Jordan , near the
border with  Iraq , to assess reserves, Al Arab Al Yawm reported.  BP will draft a detailed report on the volume of gas
reserves in the field after drilling the wells, the newspaper
reported, citing an unidentified official at the Ministry of
Energy and Mineral Resources.  To contact the reporter on this story:
